Package metaheuristics

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AntColonyOptimization
    Implementation of the Ant Colony Optimization metaheuristic.
    BeesAlgorithm
    Implementation of the Bees Colony metaheuristic.
    Genetic
    Implementation of a Genetic algorithm.
    Grasp
    Implementation of the GRASP (Greedy Randomized Adaptive Search Procedure) metaheuristic.
    Greedy
    Implementation of a greedy algorithm : NEH for permutation flow shop problems and Nearest Neighbor for TSP.
    Ils
    Implementation of the ILS (Iterated Local Search) metaheuristic.
    LocalSearch
    Implementation of a Local Search algorithm.
    Memetic
    Implementation of the Memetic metaheuristic.
    Parallel
    Solver running 4 solvers of the same type in parallel.
    SimulatedAnnealing
    Implementation of the Simulated Annealing metaheuristic.
    Solver
    Abstract class for algorithms and metaheuristics.
    TabuSearch
    Implementation of the Tabu Search metaheuristic.
    Vns
    Implementation of the VNS (Variable Neighborhood Search) metaheuristic.
    WolfPackAlgorithm
    Implementation of the Wolf Pack metaheuristic, a new algorithm designed by Arthur Godet.
